# Task 8 – Add Fields to Book Table

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task configures the Book (u_book) table by adding the required fields needed to maintain library book information.

## Fields Added

- Title (String)
- Author (String)
- ISBN (String)
- Status (Choice)

## Status Choices

- Available (Default)
- Issued
- Lost

## Steps Performed

1. Opened the Book table.
2. Accessed the Columns (Dictionary) related list.
3. Added Title, Author, ISBN, and Status fields.
4. Configured Status as a Choice field.
5. Added Available, Issued, and Lost values.
6. Set Available as the default value.
7. Verified all fields on the Book form.

## Expected Outcome

The Book table now contains all required fields for managing library books and tracking their availability.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- System Definition
- Dictionary Entries
- Choice Fields

## Status

Completed
